songs.title: Nightcrawler (Demo)
songs.lyrics:

(Turn the autotune up more)

Don't buy ’em back
Retire, I done found my friends

Can't run from what's comin' (Can't run from what's comin')

Can't run from what's comin' (Can't run from what's comin')

Always when the night calls
When the night calls
We want money, we want hoes, we want alcohol
All these hunnids, all these thousands, I'ma spend it all

I got me some money, for
